data.description:
Welcome Home! This property is located in a sought after North Fort Worth Community in Northwest ISD that has community pools, playgrounds and walking trails. You will be within walking Distance from Nance Elementary School. Open concept kitchen, carpet and laminate wood floors. Roof recently replaced as of June 2023! Home has an substantial living room with wood burning fireplace and a formal dining room. Master bedroom and bathroom with dual sinks and separate shower and garden tub. Split bedrooms for privacy. Quiet neighborhood, 15 mins away from major highway, shopping, dining and entertainment!

See Private Remarks!
